<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7742> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7742" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Praetor? in 54. See MRR 2.221, 227, note 1. Gruen (LGRR 166, note 8) identifies him with Cn. Domitius Calvinus (43), Pr. 56, and probably quaesitor in 54; cf. Shackleton Bailey, CQF 195.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5607> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5607" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Prefect of cavalry under Curio in Africa (Caes. BC 2.42.3)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5219> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5219" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Presided over the second prosecution of Caelius Rufus (Cic. QF 2.11.2)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5218> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5218" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "1 Domitius should probably be distinguished from both the Praetor of 56 (Calvinus) and the Consul of 54 (Ahenobarbus). Münzer (RE) points out that there were other Domitii of some prominence in this period (see Ascon. 54 C; Caes. BC 2.42.3; BCH 18 [1894] 419f.)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5132> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5132" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "The Domitius who presided over the trial of Caelius Rufus de vi (Cic. Cael. 32 and 70-72) may possibly be the same as the Praetor who presided over his second trial in 54, and not Cn. Domitins Calvinus, who in 56 presided over the Quaestio de ambitu (see above, on Domitius; Seidel, FA 66; Mommsen, Str. 2.584, and note 3)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertion/6285> rdfs:label "Post Assertion: #6285" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertion ;
	dprr:isAboutPerson <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/Person/2399> ;
